beer.beer_description: Introducing our West Coast IPA, generously double dry-hopped with Azacca, Idaho 7 & Strata hops. This hop trifecta delivers a burst of tropical fruit, citrus, and dank pine notes. With a crisp, clean malt backbone and a refreshing bitterness, this beer is a vibrant homage to the Pacific-Northwest's hop-rich landscapes. Dank, Piney & Resinous... Can't beat it!

items.badge_description: There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 230 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 47!
